<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-338] mds directory changed to mdt in a few places in /proc</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-338</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In Section 13.11 of the Lutre manual the line is incorrect:&lt;br/&gt;
mds1# cat /proc/fs/lustre/mds/testfs-MDT0000/recovery_status&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should be &quot;mdt&quot; instead of &quot;mds&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In section 36.19.3&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is this line&lt;br/&gt;
    /proc/fs/lustre/mds|obdfilter/*/exports/&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For the MDS this is /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/*/exports     (not &quot;mds&quot;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For obdfileer directory is only on the OSS.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;#8212;&lt;br/&gt;
also in this section:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#8226; Improved MDT statistics&lt;br/&gt;
More detailed MDT operations statistics are collected for better profiling.&lt;br/&gt;
/proc/fs/lustre/mds/*/stats&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should be &quot;mdt&quot; and not mds&quot; for the directory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
